6, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\", \"score\": 0.9983853804591941, \"rank\": 0.0016172307154118193, \"text\": \"Dad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\"}, {\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\", \"score\": 0.9999999993533493, \"rank\": 3.1014371669804177e-10, \"text\": \"Sebastian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timbaland\"}, {\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.8027302145211742, \"rank\": 0.23606685268813993, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"former Australian Open tennis champion\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"mum Regina\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"the same sport\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"son\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"the emerging names\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"the fringes\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oldest daughter Jessica has nine top 10 major golf finishes and is one of the best players around.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999944268643735, \"rank\": 5.50575973564244e-06, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nine top 10 major golf finishes\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"the best players\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then, there is Nelly - the best player in the world.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nelly\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"the best player\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to some light family competition, the stakes are incredibly high.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some light family competition\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the stakes\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We always make fun of the boys because we say that the girls in the Korda family are the only ones that are the Olympians and the boys are not,\\\" Korda said.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"the boys\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"the Korda family\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"the only ones\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympians\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"the boys\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"Korda\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, we have that above them in the family.\\\"\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Korda is in Paris for the defence of her Olympic title, and if the women's event can even generate half as much drama as the men did last week, then we are in for something special at Le Golf National.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999979490894, \"rank\": 2.0510231935377007e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Korda\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"the defence\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic title\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's event\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"half as much drama\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Golf National\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seventeen of the world's top 19 players are here this week, including more than a dozen major winners, but all eyes will be firmly fixed on Korda.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's top 19 players\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"more than a dozen major winners\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"all eyes\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"Korda\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old almost transcends her sport and this season, she has gone to spectacular heights.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"this season\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"spectacular heights\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Korda won a scarcely believable six tournaments from just eight starts, including her second major at April's Chevron Championship.\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chevron_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chevron Championship\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q15061650\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chevron_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chevron_Championship\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Korda\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"a scarcely believable six tournaments\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"just eight starts\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"her second major\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But on the third hole of her first round of the ninth event at the US Open, she unravelled spectacularly - and has been unable to knit her game back together since.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third hole\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"her first round\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"the ninth event\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"the US Open\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"her game\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Korda went into the water three times on the 12th hole, after starting on the 10th, shot a 10-over-par 80 and then missed the cut.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Korda\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"the 12th hole\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2172}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10th\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"par\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"the cut\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She followed that up with a 76 at the Meijer LPGA Classic for Simply Give, and missed the cut again, and then an 81 at the KPMG PGA Championship for a third straight early exit.\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2373, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KPMG\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KPMG\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KPMG\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KPMG\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Meijer LPGA Classic\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"Simply Give\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2323}, {\"ngram\": \"the cut\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"a third straight early exit\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From barely being able to miss, to barely being able to putt, Korda quickly announced a break ahead of theOlympicsand arrives in Paris after four weeks' rest.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2558, \"end\": 2563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999979490894, \"rank\": 2.0510231935377007e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Korda\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsand\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"four weeks' rest\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The game of golf of is a funny game,\\\" Korda said.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The game\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"a funny game\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"Korda\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes you feel on top of the world and in a matter of a couple seconds, you just feel like you are on the bottom of the sea.\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"a matter\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple seconds\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"the sea\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, it definitely makes you appreciate the good golf that you play, but yeah, I mean, you have to have a mix of everything in there and everything can not always go well.\\\"\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the good golf\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2825}, {\"ngram\": \"a mix\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2895}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's lucky, therefore, that she has the support of a family who know a thing or two about dealing with the highs and lows of elite level sport.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2993}, {\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3005}, {\"ngram\": \"a thing\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3022}, {\"ngram\": \"the highs\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3058}, {\"ngram\": \"lows\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3067}, {\"ngram\": \"elite level sport\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My parents have always said it's very important to put your head down, grind, go to the gym - but it's also important to recharge your battery,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My parents\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"your head\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"your battery\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because sometimes with all the obligations you maybe have off the golf course, and all the emotions you feel on the golf course, all the adrenaline, it tears at you a little bit.\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the obligations\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"the golf course\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"the golf course\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"all the adrenaline\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's good to kind of step away and recharge your batteries and come back a little bit fresher.\\\"\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of step\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3456}, {\"ngram\": \"your batteries\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Korda tees off at 9.55am, in the group just after Charley Hull, the world number eight who is spearheading Team GB's charge alongside Georgia Hall.\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3578, \"end\": 3590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Hull\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charley Hull\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Hull\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Hull\"}, {\"begin\": 3635, \"end\": 3642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999998276416739, \"rank\": 1.0927435084798684e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Korda\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3533}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3566}, {\"ngram\": \"the world number\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"Georgia Hall\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After missing out in Tokyo, Hull - who finished seventh in Rio - is excited to be back in red, white, and blue, except for one minor snag.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3698, \"end\": 3703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9672801366890553, \"rank\": 0.03380371538530954, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hull\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3739}, {\"ngram\": \"one minor snag\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do smoke on the course,\\\" she said on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 3864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a habit but I will not do this week.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a habit\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, it is just something I do.\\\"\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just something\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smoking is banned from all Olympic venues and athletes are no exception, which is a problem for Hull - who went viral earlier this year when images of her puffing away on the course went viral.\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 4136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smoking\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"all Olympic venues\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3984}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 3997}, {\"ngram\": \"no exception\", \"from\": 4002, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4034}, {\"ngram\": \"Hull\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"images\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4090}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Will it affect her?\", \"from\": 4138, \"to\": 4157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it will,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because it relaxes me a little bit.\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is what it is.\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being able to play in the Olympics is a dream.\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4270, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am excited for that and also meeting new athletes that I may not have had the chance to meet.\\\"\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new athletes\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4348}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch every moment of Olympic GamesParis 2024live only ondiscovery+, the streaming home of the Olympics Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4551, \"end\": 4562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6064659786032325e-13, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic GamesParis\", \"from\": 4417, \"to\": 4435}, {\"ngram\": \"the streaming home\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4482}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics Join thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4535}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 4578, \"to\": 4591}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 4607, \"to\": 4615}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4643}, {\"ngra